<section
	data-section="login"
	class="mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl space-y-6 rounded-[32px] border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/50 p-6 text-white shadow-[0_30px_120px_rgba(0,0,0,0.55)] backdrop-blur-2xl sm:p-8 lg:p-10"
>
	<div class="space-y-3">
		<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-sky-200">Arquivo Inteligente</p>
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight">
			Faça login para acessar o painel do arquivo.
		</h1>
		<p class="text-base text-white/70">
			Autenticação obrigatória garante rastreabilidade das movimentações e evita acessos não
			autorizados.
		</p>
	</div>
	<article class="space-y-6 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 p-6 shadow-inner shadow-white/5">
		<div class="space-y-2">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Acesso seguro</h2>
			<p class="text-white/70">Informe usuário e senha para desbloquear as funções.</p>
		</div>
		<form id="login-form" class="space-y-5">
			<label class="space-y-2 text-sm text-white/80">
				<span>Usuário</span>
				<input
					type="text"
					id="login-identifier"
					placeholder="admin"
					autocomplete="username"
					required
					class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder:text-white/40 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-sky-400"
				/>
			</label>
			<label class="space-y-2 text-sm text-white/80">
				<span>Senha</span>
				<input
					type="password"
					id="login-password"
					placeholder="•••••••"
					required
					class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder:text-white/40 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-sky-400"
				/>
			</label>
			<button
				type="submit"
				class="mt-1 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-cyan-400 px-4 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/30 transition hover:brightness-110 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-cyan-300 sm:mt-2"
			>
				Entrar
			</button>
			<span id="auth-error" class="text-sm text-rose-300" hidden></span>
		</form>
	</article>
</section>
